Just ran the script and got this result:
```

- TensorFlow is installed at: D:\Programs\Anaconda3.6\lib\site-packages\tensorflow
The thread 'MainThread' (0x12f8) has exited with code 0 (0x0).
The program '[7320] python.exe' has exited with code -1 (0xffffffff).
```
I installed the new version of tensorflow for python 3.6
